    "body_text": [
        {
            "text": ". SFS is shown (a) for the IFNL4 region including the 3' and 5' UTRs (chr19:39736954--39739496) and (b) for the control regions (pseudogenes, see text below). The SFS is based on 50 individuals for each of the popula1ons but PUR (44 individuals). We show three popula1ons per con1nent.",
