        {
            "text": "As the transcript with the \u0394G allele encodes a func1onal protein, we assessed whether puta1vely func1onal variants in this haplotype show signatures of natural selec1on. To inves1gate such a scenario we analyzed the signature of selec1on for the three described non--synonymous variants in IFNL4 [14] , all residing on the \u0394G haplotype. To avoid a confounding impact of the TT haplotype we condi1oned on the \u0394G haplotype and calculated F ST , XP--EHH and iHS. No signature of natural selec1on for any of the variants was observed (data not shown). However, all of them are in such low frequencies that these tests have very low power [15, 16] . Thus we can not",
